<div><span class="c925-kicker">First Physical Issue</span>
<h1 class="c925-title">CIRCUS925 Founding Drop</h1>
<p class="c925-subtitle">A limited preorder-backed production campaign for CIR000, apparel, cassette editions, archive material, and future physical formats.</p>
<div class="c925-actions"><a class="c925-button" href="#support-options">View Supporter Tiers</a> <a class="c925-button secondary" href="#campaign-objects">View Campaign Objects</a></div>
</div>
<div class="c925-hero-art">
