</div>
</section>
<section class="c925-section" aria-label="Campaign summary">
<div class="c925-meta-grid">
<div class="c925-meta-item"><span class="c925-meta-label">Campaign Goal</span> <span class="c925-meta-value">$5,000</span></div>
<div class="c925-meta-item"><span class="c925-meta-label">Model</span> <span class="c925-meta-value">No-debt production</span></div>
<div class="c925-meta-item"><span class="c925-meta-label">Focus</span> <span class="c925-meta-value">Vinyl, apparel, cassette, artifacts</span></div>
</div>
</section>
<section id="campaign-story" class="c925-section">
<div class="c925-two-col">
<div>
<h2 class="c925-section-title">A first material cycle.</h2>
</div>
<div>
<p class="c925-copy">CIRCUS925 begins with a focused first physical issue: CIR000, limited apparel, cassette editions, printed matter, archive material, and experimental object research.</p>
<p class="c925-copy">This is not a donation campaign. It is a direct exchange between the label and its early supporters. Each tier gives supporters something tangible in return while helping fund the final production stage of the first CIRCUS925 release cycle.</p>
<p class="c925-copy">Artist fees, branding, and design have already been paid independently. Campaign proceeds go toward vinyl production, apparel, merch, packaging, fulfillment, payment processing, release support, and selected physical-format research.</p>
</div>
</section>
<section class="c925-section">
<h2 class="c925-section-title">What funds cover</h2>
<p class="c925-copy">Funds from this campaign support the first CIRCUS925 production cycle: pressing CIR000, producing physical artifacts, launching the first limited apparel run, developing cassette editions, and researching future low-waste packaging and insert concepts.</p>
<div class="c925-breakdown">
<div class="c925-breakdown-item"><strong>Vinyl</strong>Lacquer, plating, pressing, labels, sleeves, freight</div>
<div class="c925-breakdown-item"><strong>Apparel</strong>First-run CIRCUS925 shirt and wearable objects</div>
<div class="c925-breakdown-item"><strong>Artifacts</strong>Cassettes, stickers, patches, prints, slipmats, totes</div>
<div class="c925-breakdown-item"><strong>Fulfillment</strong>Packaging, shipping materials, payment fees, release support</div>
</div>
</section>

