<section class="c925-section">
<div class="c925-two-col">
<div>
<h2 class="c925-section-title">Higher-level support</h2>
</div>
<div>
<p class="c925-copy">Consulting, design support, and founding patron options are available by inquiry. These are intentionally limited so the scope remains focused and deliverable.</p>
<div class="c925-card-grid">
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>Label / Release Consulting</h3>
<p>For artists, DJs, small labels, and organizers who need practical help with vinyl release planning, direct preorder strategy, release budgeting, distribution, or label startup structure.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>Design / Identity Support</h3>
