<h2 class="c925-section-title">Campaign roadmap</h2>
</div>
<div class="c925-timeline">
<div class="c925-step">
<h3>Phase 1 — Campaign preview</h3>
<p>Landing page, supporter tiers, product mockups, and early access list.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-step">
<h3>Phase 2 — Preorder window</h3>
<p>A focused 14–21 day preorder window to validate demand and determine production scale.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-step">
<h3>Phase 3 — Production lock</h3>
<p>Confirm quantities, finalize vinyl production, apparel, artifacts, cassette, and fulfillment materials.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-step">
<h3>Phase 4 — Fulfillment and documentation</h3>
<p>Ship supporter orders, document the production process, and use campaign results for future grants, sponsors, lenders, and partners.</p>
