<section class="c925-section">
<h2 class="c925-section-title">FAQ</h2>
<div class="c925-card-grid">
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>Is this a donation campaign?</h3>
<p>No. This is a preorder-backed production campaign. Every supporter tier includes a direct return: a record, artifact, archive access, apparel, cassette, collector item, or service.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>When will items ship?</h3>
<p>Some items may ship earlier than others. Reserved records ship once production and delivery are complete. Updates will be shared with campaign supporters.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>What is CIR000?</h3>
<p>CIR000 is the first CIRCUS925 physical release cycle and the center of the founding campaign.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>What is Tape Dispatch?</h3>
<p>Tape Dispatch is a limited cassette mixtape series connected to CIRCUS925 / SSS DJ culture, influences, and archive material.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>What is the private archive download?</h3>
<p>A private supporter-only transmission of selected archive material. It is not a streaming pivot or full digital release.</p>
</div>
<div class="c925-card">
<h3>What is the mycelium edition?</h3>
<p>A limited research-focused edition supporting a dried, finished, non-living biomaterial insert or documented sustainable-material prototype. Final material may vary depending on feasibility.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
